== 争议、评论与影响 ==
对于珠宝被梁丽“捡走”，一方面珠宝员工在公众场合不注意保管财物导致不见的行为受到批评和质疑，认为其也有责任。而另外一方面，对梁丽在捡到珠宝之后被没有打开并使用，但对其之前没有主动上交而是警察来查才主动上交珠宝这一过程是侵占罪还是盗窃罪、甚至是无罪之争。<ref>{{Cite web|title=深圳检察院承诺公正办理梁丽案 暂未定|url=http://news.sohu.com/20090513/n263924512.shtml|accessdate=2009-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090516061016/http://news.sohu.com/20090513/n263924512.shtml|archive-date=2009-05-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 民众、学者对梁丽的案件持续关注，对梁丽该不该判刑<ref>{{cite web|title=有罪还是无罪？专家学者深度解读梁丽涉嫌盗窃案|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/legal/2009-05/21/content_11411653.htm|accessdate=2009-06-23|date=2009年5月21日|publisher=法制日报|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090530082416/http://news.xinhuanet.com/legal/2009-05/21/content_11411653.htm|archive-date=2009-05-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=公民“捡”东西的权利不能被剥夺|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/local/2009-05/13/content_11365944.htm|accessdate=2009-06-23|date=2009-05-13|publisher=郑州晚报|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090516232409/http://news.xinhuanet.com/local/2009-05/13/content_11365944.htm|archive-date=2009-05-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>、该不该以“盗窃罪”论罪<ref>{{cite web|title=是“捡”是“占”还是“盗”？|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2009-05-18/071215641075s.shtml|accessdate=2009-06-23|date=2009年5月18日|publisher=大河网|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304125247/http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2009-05-18/071215641075s.shtml|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>、是否应以“侵占罪”判刑<ref>{{Cite web|title=搜狐侃事：“捡”个东西判无期，又一个许霆案？|url=http://news.sohu.com/20090511/n263879570.shtml|accessdate=2009-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090513085552/http://news.sohu.com/20090511/n263879570.shtml|archive-date=2009-05-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=梁丽构成侵占罪|url=http://www.legaldaily.com.cn/2007fxy/2009-06/10/content_1103251.htm|accessdate=2009-06-23|date=2009-06-10|publisher=法制网}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=从刑事法治视角看“梁丽案”|url=http://www.legaldaily.com.cn/2007ajzj/2009-05/27/content_1096333.htm|accessdate=2009-06-23|author=[[赵秉志|赵秉志]]|date=2009-05-27|publisher=法制日报|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090925033755/http://www.legaldaily.com.cn/2007ajzj/2009-05/27/content_1096333.htm|archive-date=2009-09-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>等问题进行讨论。

